deck: Superman of earth-34
description:
The last son of the ancient super-civilization Mu, sent into the future to escape their dying past, Savior is the founder and leader of the Light Brigade and a defender of Cosmoville on earth 34.

He also helped in the defeat of Mandarkk as member of the Supermen of the Multiverse.

He is a homage to Astro City's Samaritan.
